case.title: Something Different - 21
case.text: I'm 21 and dominate, open minded, free spirited girl. Im AA, 5'11 and a solid 230lbs. Just looking for a real man to start a friendship and see where it goes (: write jojo in the subj line so I know you're real. Looks is something I'm least concerned about as long as you're genuine with a banging personality. We can go places <3 your pic gets mines.
